  <!-- EN: A prototype particle lance. Its reactor is replaced with a stabilized microscopic skipgate linked to the core of a nearby star. Its beam ignores any armor and cause explosions upon contact. -->
  <CMC_TaoTie_Persona.description>一把跨时代的射线步枪，其发射的高能粒子束可以造成巨额伤害。该武器在近距离对抗装甲目标时极具优势。\n\n-散热器：该武器拥有散热器，在热量条满后将无法射击。\n-DEW扫射转移：会在消灭当前目标后转向攻击临近目标，转移过程中会额外消耗连射次数。</CMC_TaoTie_Persona.description>
  <!-- EN: barrel -->
  <CMC_TaoTie_Persona.tools.barrel.label>枪管</CMC_TaoTie_Persona.tools.barrel.label>
